To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private UniqueThreeRiver _uniquethreeriver;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_uniquethreeriver = UniqueThreeRiver(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_uniquethreeriver.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "period", _uniquethreeriver.Period);
    Plot("My Indicators", "uniquethreeriver", _uniquethreeriver.Current);
}
